      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ASTON RAMONA (7) was safely held last time out, finishing sixth at this track over 400m behind Compton Franky (24.16) in a Other. Was in the money prior to that. Goes well out of this box with a win and two minor placings. Better than the latest effort and deserves another chance. ACOUSTIC FLASH (1) was responsible for a modest effort most recently when seventh at Geelong over 400m behind It's Soysages (23.72) in a Grade 5. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and five minor placings to her credit. Can measure up this time. ROCKET SUSIE (8) doesn't win out of turn. Hit the board with a minor placing last time when second (18.44) at this track. Solid record here winning three races. Winning chance. MOCAMBORA MIA (4) cannot be written off despite a miss here at her latest outing.",
